name: College Together
description:
College Together is an entirely new college experience where youth earn an accelerated college degree and learn professional skills in a supportive job placement at the same time. Without having to choose between working on learning, they finish a degree in as little as a year and earn an income instead of taking on debt- all while in a learning community with daily mentorship and holistic support. 

https://www.collegetogether.org/

This organization is part of the Philadelphia Justice and Equity Fellowship
